Q.3 Write php script which will find out character count of particular
character in string.
Ans :
<body>
<form method="post">
Enter the String : <input type="text" name="inp1"/><hr/>
Enter the Character to check : <input type="text"
name="inp2"/><hr/>
<input type="submit" value="Check"/>
</form>
</body>
<?php if
($_POST) {

$string = $_POST['inp1'];
$character = $_POST['inp2'];

$count = substr_count($string, $character);

echo "The character $character appears $count times in the string
$string.";
}

?>
