Q.4 Write php script to find sum of digits of given no?
Ans :
<body>
<form method="post">

Enter the Number : <input type="text" name="num"/><hr/>
<input type="submit" value="Submit"/>
</form>
</body>

<?php
$num = $_POST["num"];
$sum = 0; $rem = 0; for ($i = 0;
$i <= strlen($num); $i++) { $rem
= $num % 10;
$sum = $sum + $rem;

$num = $num / 10; } echo
"Sum of digits is $sum";
?>
