Q.6 Write php script to check given no is prime or not.

Ans :

<body>
<form method="post">
Enter the Number : <input type="text" name="nm1"/><hr/>

<input type="submit" value="Submit"/>
</form>
</body> <?php
function
check_prime($num)
{ if ($num == 1) return 0;
for ($i = 2; $i <= $num/2; $i++)
{ if ($num % $i == 0)
return 0; } return
1; }

$num = $_POST["nm1"];
$flag_val = check_prime($num);

if ($flag_val == 1) echo $num ." is a
prime number"; else echo $num ." is
NOT a prime number"

?>
